</figure>

<main>

    <section class="wrapper text-center py-24 grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 md:text-left">

        <article>

            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-very-dark-blue mb-6 md:text-4xl">Why Choose PatientNexus?
            </h2>

            <p class="text-dark-grayish-blue">Track patient progress and outcomes from initial consultation to follow-up.</p>

        </article>

        <div class="grid gap-12">

            <article class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6">

                <p class="bg-very-pale-red rounded-l-full font-bold flex items-center md:bg-transparent">
                    <span class="bg-sky-400 text-white px-6 rounded-full py-2">
                        01
                    </span>
                    <span class="flex-1 p-2">
                        Enhanced collaboration
                    </span>
                </p>

                <p class="text-dark-grayish-blue text-left">Improve communication and coordination between doctors, assistants, and patients. Our system provides a central platform for sharing information and updates.</p>

            </article>

            <article class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6">

                <p class="bg-very-pale-red rounded-l-full font-bold flex items-center md:bg-transparent">
                    <span class="bg-sky-400 text-white px-6 rounded-full py-2">
                        02
                    </span>
                    <span class="flex-1 p-2">
                        Automated workflows
                    </span>
                </p>

                <p class="text-dark-grayish-blue text-left">Streamline administrative tasks and improve efficiency with automated appointment scheduling, laboratory result tracking, and more.

                </p>

            </article>

            <article class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6">

                <p class="bg-very-pale-red rounded-l-full font-bold flex items-center md:bg-transparent">
                    <span class="bg-sky-400 text-white px-6 rounded-full py-2">
                        03
                    </span>
                    <span class="flex-1 p-2">
                        Comprehensive patient management
                    </span>
                </p>

                <p class="text-dark-grayish-blue text-left">Manage all patient information in one place. From medical history to appointment scheduling, our system provides a centralized hub for all patient data.

                </p>

            </article>


        </div>

    </section>


    <section class="wrapper text-center py-24 max-w-lg mx-auto md:max-w-xl">

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-very-dark-blue md:text-4xl">What Our Users Say
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-24 mb-14">

            <article class="bg-vary-light-gray pt-16 pb-12 px-4 relative">

                <img src="./images/avatar-ali.png" class="absolute w-24 aspect-square -top-12 inset-x-0 mx-auto">

                <h3 class="text-xl mb-4 pt-2 font-bold text-very-dark-blue">Aria Petrov
                </h3>

                <p class="text-dark-grayish-blue">“Since implementing PatientNexus, we've seen a significant improvement in patient satisfaction and reduced administrative errors.”</p>

            </article>

        </div>

        <a asp-controller="User" asp-action="Index" class="button mx-auto shadow-xl shadow-sky-200/30">Get Started</a>
